channel.title: Thought I'd let you know of some jackass
channel.description:
Hey this goes in this section because it involves p server development, and is helping by warning you of this ridiculous person.
This kid, who called himself "Mod Taharok", asked me to make a server for him, I said no. This was his response.
http://img360.imageshack.us/my.php?image=noobdb6.jpg [IMG]http://i224.photobucket.com/albums/dd149/tjrazor/noob.jpg[/img]
ROFL
EDIT: [size=25pt]I thought this was obvious, but apparently not. This is in no way meant to be derogatory towards Taharok. The person in this was NOT him, rather an impersonator.[/size]
